  * Headless-JavaFX support: bin/xvfbrun, bin/snapshot, ScreenshotDriver.
  * arbshell wrapper: forward classpath to jshell driver and remote
    agent; strip jshell -R-prefixed JPMS flags.
  * Javadoc: skip by default (opt in with -Djavadoc.skip=false), make
    failures non-fatal, switch to <subpackages>, exclude arb.solvers.
  * Gaussian-process sampler: runtime sample-length control bar; default
